name: Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader
original_name: Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader
overview: The hit game show where adults have to answer grade-school level questions to win big is back! And this time, the kids play a bigger role as they help contestants prove that they're smarter than a 5th grader.

episodes.name: 3rd Grade Teacher
episodes.overview: An educator aims to prove herself to her students. But when she’s stumped in 3rd grade, she considers breaking all school rules and cheating off the class!

episodes.name: Catholic School Teacher
episodes.overview: A nun walks into a classroom…and is sure she can ace elementary school! With the help of these 5th graders, will she dance her way up the money ladder?

episodes.name: Elementary School Principal
episodes.overview: A school administrator is confident, but it doesn’t take long for the class to totally school him! Will he actually cheat to get through the 5th grade?

episodes.name: Emergency Operator
episodes.overview: This 911 dispatcher is used to dealing with stress, but will the 5th grade be too much for her to handle?

episodes.name: Agriculturalist
episodes.overview: An urban farmer puts his brain to the test by answering questions and taking the final exam for his chance to win $100,000!

episodes.name: Registered Nurse
episodes.overview: A licensed medic is put to the test and it isn’t long before he considers using a cheat! Will he leave his fate in the hands of a 5th grader?

episodes.name: Astronaut
episodes.overview: This contestant has traveled to outer space, so he’s confident he can land on $100,000. He blasts through the questions, but feels the pressure along the way. He even considers cheating when he gets lost in the 5th grade!

episodes.name: Firefighter
episodes.overview: This contestant fights fires for a living, but will the heat in the classroom be too much for him to take?

episodes.name: Doctor
episodes.overview: A medical practitioner thinks she has enough degrees to ace elementary school, but she only gets to 2nd grade before she considers using a cheat!

episodes.name: Marine Expert
episodes.overview: A shark diver plunges into the classroom and finds herself in the deep end! Will she cheat to save her chances of winning big?

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: This high-flyer is sure he will soar his way through elementary school. But when he runs out of a gas, he might consider cheating sooner rather than later!

episodes.name: Personal Trainer
episodes.overview: A fitness instructor is confident he’s strong enough to climb his way up the money ladder! But will he be able to keep up with these 5th graders?

episodes.name: Zookeeper
episodes.overview: This animal expert aims to prove she’s brainy enough to ace the 5th grade! She likes a team effort, but will she cheat for a chance at $100,000?

episodes.name: College Dean
episodes.overview: An Ivy League professor aims to prove his years of schooling haven’t gone to waste. But when his big brain starts to overthink, he considers cheating off a 5th grader!

episodes.name: Policeman
episodes.overview: This law enforcement officer is all about following the rules until he’s caught without an answer! Will he cheat to move up the money ladder?

episodes.name: EMT
episodes.overview: An emergency technician stays calm under pressure and fights her way through the 4th grade. But she’s not afraid to ask for a classmate’s help in the 5th grade!

episodes.name: 6th Grade Teacher
episodes.overview: A schoolteacher is convinced she can ace elementary school, but when a question stumps her early on, she’ll consider cheating much earlier than she expected.

episodes.name: Truck Driver
episodes.overview: This transporter is used to working alone, but it isn’t long before she decides she needs the help of these 5th graders!

episodes.name: Football Coach
episodes.overview: A gridiron great is ready to tackle elementary school! But when he’s brain blocked in the 3rd grade, he just might have to cheat to be competitive in the game.

episodes.name: Behavioral Scientist
episodes.overview: A brain expert puts her own mind to the test by answering questions and taking the final exam for her chance to win $100,000!
